  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1270006/" class="title-link">好书，就是太贵</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1270006"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/elact/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1123727-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/elact/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Elact</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-12-29"
      class="main-meta">2007-12-29 16:00:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1270006_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  那天在书店看到了本书，挺好的，就是价格吓人。2本59元。59对于书的内容来说不贵，不过作者都已经过世好几千年了，出版社不用给稿费，不用给版税，这个价格对用户来说是不是黑了点？  建议去当当或者卓越搜本书的其他版本，价格在10多元，同样的东西。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1270006/#comments">(8回应)</a>
