  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8037948">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8037948/" class="title-link">武经七书读后有感</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8037948"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/147147635/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u147147635-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/147147635/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">深藏功与名</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-08-11"
      class="main-meta">2016-08-11 10:35:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8037948_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  武经七书，每日一书，先对比孙子兵法和吴子兵法。 总体来说，孙子兵法重战略，吴子兵法重战术，所以今人多推崇孙子，少有人推崇吴子，然而势与术同样重要，只重势，不重术，则早晚失势，只重术，不重势，则事倍功半，或者压根就不能成功。 作为古老的兵法，兵法对于今天组织的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8037948_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8037948_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





